Bcc: jose.bestard@enron.com, fred.sampaio@enron.com, debora.klinger@enron.com
X-From: Luiz Maurer
X-To: Sergio Assad, Richard Shapiro
X-cc: Jose Bestard, Fred Sampaio, Debora Klinger
